Like if you want 2 edit the last object (Bankz)

Just change the following

makeGlobalObject(xxxx, yyyy, --ID--, 0, 10); // bankz

xxxx = X Cordinate yyyy = Y Cordinate --ID-- Like 2213 (Bank)

Change the numbers , save it and compile your server.

Restart it and it should work !
